        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在常压、400°C条件下，使用Pd-Ni/SBA-16双金属催化剂，对α-四氢萘酮进行气相加氢脱氧反应，生成顺式/反式十氢萘、四氢萘和α-四氢萘醇等喷气燃料范围烃类。最高选择性（88.21%）获得异构化产物反式十氢萘。",
        "text_snippet": "Vapour phase hydrodeoxygenation of a-tetralone was carried out under ambient pressure and the highest selectivity (88.21%) for the isomerized product trans-decalin was obtained.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
